INTRO
-----
This program is a tool for linux server administrators for them to configure 
their web servers more easily.

DESCRIPTION
---------------------------
ServerEach is intended both for people with deep understanding of apache and bind 
server configurations and for people who want just easily to configure basic 
settings and start using their own web server (for ex. dedicated server).
  
INSTALLATION
------------
1. Place the ServerEach folder in /opt/servereach
2. As root execute /opt/servereach/start script
3. Open your browser and navigate to server-address.com:10011
4. It will ask for username and password. Login with you system's root account.
